{"tid":406712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"能印出「所有中文字」的印章 (發揚正體字）","createTime":"2017-09-20T01:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T04:07:43.000Z","uid":89349,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1051cd4c2cf8bba4ebbe847e513705f30eef871b","tid":406712,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/091459_4182e67d20994b6ddfba9c04fb1588ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F091459_4182e67d20994b6ddfba9c04fb1588ff.jpg&h=4d33ee0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/091459_dbd9d4efcac532e46a90023c4fce1190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F091459_dbd9d4efcac532e46a90023c4fce1190.jpg&h=696e8822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國人常說中文繁體字架構複雜，可是說到底都不過是橫（一）、直（丨）、撇（丿）、點（丶）、捺（㇏）、折（乛）的組合<br />\n<br />\n兩名少女憑著創意設計了六個印章，即可組合成所有中文字，既實用，又可隨心發揮親手印出不同風格和顏色的美術字，這樣學中文，想必更添樂趣﹗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01aa5693a327cbeaaa5863d1e4ffa517e1c7dfc7","tid":406712,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957f4f5563c0d82ed703d4083ee13dc874578e59","tid":406712,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:24:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f56055301e6da7cc7a77569353ac8686a3ec1d87","tid":406712,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:25:01.000Z","msg":"兩個女仔好似唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"